---
title: Spring Pesto Pasta with Tomatoes, Zucchini and Leeks
description: Light, fresh and lemony, this pasta celebrates delicate basil with a buttery pesto sauce and fresh leaves torn over top. A sprinkling of Parm brings it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pates-printanieres-au-pesto-f6415a5f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/spring-pesto-pasta-622f2228a8b64256944e8b43-0403e240.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
